      "raw_text": "For purpose of opening the re-\ngion bordering on Moses lake, in\nDouglas county, where 100000\nacres can be irrigated, the North\nern Pacific will construct a line\nfrom Adrian on the Great Northern\nline to Pasco, passing through\nOthello on the Milwaukee line.\n\n\nThis announcement was made to-\nday by President Elliott of the\nNorthern Pacific, who is in Seattle\ncompleting sale of the lands of the\ncompany in Washington.\n\n\nThe line will be an important\nfeeder to the Northern Pacific, for\nit will give an outlet to all wheat\ntonnage from the Big Bend country\ninstead of sending it back to Che\nney or over the mountains by trans\nfer to the Great Northern. ~. i =."
